It's very easy to quit when difficulty is hard. It is also very easy to feel like quitting when difficulty feels very difficult. It is also difficult for me to quit when things are difficult. No matter how difficult, it will remain. Therefore everything is difficult, making the difficulty not as difficult as they appear or seem. 
Digital abstract expression using photoshop paint.
